title: VA - Achtung Chicago!  Zwei! (1993) - [v2]
description: Chicago, US based punk/hardcore label started by Russ Forster in 1986. At the end of the 1980's, Forster handed control over to a collective made up of Douglas Ward, Ben Weasel, and John Pierson. Ben and John soon dropped out but Douglas remained with the label until it's demise in the late 1990s. The label put out an array of records from Chicago-based punk, hardcore, and emo bands and is best known for it's 3 "Achtung Chicago" compilations. This is the first 2 comps
